The Transformer is proposed as an alternative to existing sequence transduction models.

Ashish Vaswani	Transformer
developer, contributor
Ashish Vaswani designed and implemented the first Transformer models.

Noam Shazeer	Transformer
developer, contributor
Noam Shazeer proposed scaled dot-product attention, multi-head attention, and the parameter-free position representation for the Transformer.

Niki Parmar	Transformer
developer, contributor
Niki Parmar designed, implemented, tuned and evaluated countless model variants for the Transformer.
